  <brief_title>The Influence of Remote Ischemic Preconditioning on Acute Kidney Injury After Cardiac Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Influence of Remote Ischemic Preconditioning on Acute Kidney Injury After Cardiac Surgery</official_title>
